> @teknoraver suggested me that the solution is `sysctl -w net.netfilter.nf_conntrack_icmp_timeout=2`. Could you try if that solve the issue for you?

@giuseppe that works! 

Do we know why this has changed from 4.20.x kernel behavior?  Why does it affect only podman containers and not docker containers or the host directly?  Is this something that needs to be fixed for podman?
